&lt;p&gt;Adds a ShutdownHook class that is package private to regionserver.  Manages the running of the regionserver shutdown before running the fs shutdown hook.  New class has a main so its easy to check stuff works against the different hadoops; 0.20, 0.21 and cloudera 0.20.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;This addresses bug hbase-2725.&lt;br/&gt;
